LatexCommand cite
key "ChaiKaus2019,KausSA"
literal "false"

\end_inset

, marginalised religious groups in India
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "ZahraIndia"
literal "false"

\end_inset

 and regions of erstwhile East Germany
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "FrieheGermany"
literal "false"

\end_inset

) in the economies are observed to spend differently on visible items compared
 to others in a similar income group.
 That the consumers use consumption to form and maintain identities is also
 supported by the studies in marketing
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "JacksonConsIdent1999"
literal "false"

\end_inset

 and political economy
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "KoutsobinasStatusPoliticalEconomy"
literal "false"

\end_inset

